    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>A synthetic wax made by catalytic polymerization of low molecular weight, high-density ethylene. It may be used as a reversible protective coating in many applications including the conservation of outdoor sculpture.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
